name: Donate2Ukraine & Get an NFT
description:
This project is designed to donate to Ukraine and help common people there under the appeals from Vitalik Buterin and Mykhailo Fedorov, the Vice Prime Minister of Ukraine. Related links include: https://twitter.com/FedorovMykhailo/status/1497549813205848068; https://twitter.com/VitalikButerin/status/1497608588822466563.

Make love, not war. 

70% of the funding will be donated the address shown on Mykhailo Fedorov's twitter: 0x165CD37b4C644C2921454429E7F9358d18A45e14

25% would be used to supply the liquidity on Uniswap.

5% would be reserved to maintain the DAO to offer a longterm support to Ukrainian people.

Every donator will receive an NFT medal to honor their support.
